&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and maintain dashboards in SQL and BI tools (Power BI, Looker, or equivalent)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor teammates and cross-functional partners on analytical best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion data governance, documentation, and quality across the analytics function&lt;/l

