&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;You will work across Clinical Operations, Site Operations, Trial Enrollment, Business Development, and Corporate Functions, identifying high-impact opportunities and owning them from concept through deployment and adoption. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;This role reports to the Product organization and partners closely with Engineering, Data Science, Security, and Operational Leadership teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
